description: [``botocore``] AWS App Runner adds .NET 6, Go 1, PHP 8.1 and Ruby 3.1 runtimes.
[``botocore``] This release includes CertificateBasedAuthProperties in CreateDirectoryConfig and UpdateDirectoryConfig.
